"barcode and it will automatic update the Shipment Status"
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda telah menghubungkan pemindai kode batang Anda, silakan pindai "
"langsung ke kode batang dan itu akan secara otomatis memperbarui Status "
"Pengiriman"

#: admin/templates/transfer.tpl.php:25
msgid ""
"If you don't have a barcode scanner please input it to the tracking number "
"field and press Enter on your keyboard"
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda tidak memiliki pemindai kode batang, masukkan ke bidang nomor "
"pelacakan dan tekan Enter pada keyboard Anda"

#. Plugin Name of the plugin/theme
msgid "WPCargo Branches Add-ons"
msgstr "Add-on Cabang WPCargo"

#. Plugin URI of the plugin/theme
msgid "http://wpcargo.com/"
msgstr "http://wpcargo.com/"

#. Description of the plugin/theme
msgid ""
"This will add the lists of other branches on admin dashbard and generate "
"shipment tracking number base on the Branches. This will work well with "
"WPCargo Receiving Add-ons."
msgstr ""
"Ini akan menambahkan daftar cabang lain di dashbard admin dan menghasilkan "
"nomor pelacakan pengiriman berdasarkan Cabang. Ini akan bekerja dengan baik "
"dengan WPCargo Menerima Add-on."

